title: Watch: Kids try dinners from around the world and don't hold back their disgust
text:
If you're from any of the countries mentioned and have strong feelings about your national cuisine, we apologise in advance.
Cut have made a name for themselves getting kids to try different foods and talking to their parents about 'the birds and the bees' amongst other topics, and while it may not be everyone's cup of tea, you can't say the reactions aren't adorable.
Via Cut
